scene.message:
Mark: Listen, little Maki,{nl}
we wanna save Sonomura.{nl}
Can you do something?{waitkey}I know it sounds weird.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Aki is trying to{nl}
erase this world...{waitkey}Aki went off to the{nl}
worst me of all.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: The worst me is{nl}
called Pandora...{waitkey}Aki undid Pandora's seal.{waitkey}{clearbox}Swallowed up by Pandora,{nl}
Aki is trying to erase{nl}
this world - even though{waitkey}the real me will die too...

Nanjo: The school!{nl}
Beyond that door in the{nl}
library. That's it, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Mm-hm.{nl}
But to get in there, you{nl}
need the three compacts{waitkey}and the power of the{nl}
healthy me.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: {ctl0f:1}, you've got{nl}
two of them, right?{nl}
Red and green... one short.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: {ctl08:65281}Didn't you have{nl}
two? Red and green...{nl}
we're one short.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl08:65281}Didn't you have{nl}
two? Red and green?{nl}
That's one short!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1}, didn't you{nl}
have two? Red and green?{nl}
That's one short!

Nanjo: Where's the last{nl}
compact, and the ideal{nl}
Sonomura?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: There's a{nl}
Maki beyond this door too?...{nl}
I'm coming as well!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: We've come this far.{nl}
We good, everyone?{nl}
Then let's go, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{ret}

I'm the one who should{nl}
apologize... I'm sorry.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm the ideal Maki{nl}
Sonomura, after all.{nl}
I can't keep moping.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, tell me where the{nl}
last compact is.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Mm-hm.{nl}
The third compact is held{nl}
by the real me.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: The real Sonomura?{nl}
If it's hers, that's the{nl}
green one, right?{waitkey}{ctl0f:1}'s got that one, yeah?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That's the one from{nl}
the real world. Right now{nl}
the real me's consciousness{waitkey}is at Araya's Rock Cave.{nl}
The last one is held by{nl}
the real me's mind.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: From here on, I want{nl}
to manage on my own...{nl}
I've got friends to help me,{waitkey}so I'll be okay.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Maki...{nl}
All right... Be sure to{nl}
come back to me.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Mm-hm...{nl}
Be careful, me...{waitkey}{clearbox}When the three compacts{nl}
are together, chant the{nl}
spell before Pandora's door.{waitkey}

Maki: Mai-chan is me too,{nl}
isn't she...{waitkey}{clearbox}I was...{wait_fr:88} pretty cute{nl}
when I was little, huh.{nl}
Saying it myself? Heh.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Man, my head's{nl}
getting all tangled up.{nl}
How many Sonomuras ARE there?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh... so Sonomura{nl}
was cute even as a{nl}
little kid.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Truly a dialogue{nl}
with oneself. A strange{nl}
sight indeed.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...What?{wait_fr:88}{nl}
I've got a "gentle face"?{nl}
Save the jokes for your mug.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...What?{nl}
My "mouth is smiling"?!{nl}
Don't get the wrong idea!{waitkey}I've got a toothache.{waitkey}{ret}
